Detective Patrick Cherry has been stripped of his badge and gun and will be placed on administrative duty . 
  Cherry was caught on video screaming at an Uber driver in the West Village . 
  He appears on NBC tonight to 'sincerely apologize' for the outburst . 
  The video was viewed more than three million times on YouTube . 
  Detective Cherry was in plainclothes and was trying to park his car when the driver honked his horn . 
  He pulled over the cab and launched into a tirade at the driver . 
  The officer has been placed on modified duty and will lose his shield and gun . 
 